data.description: Welcome to 206 Bowline Drive a light-filled home with an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The first floor features gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the living and dining areas. Cook meals in the spacious kitchen while still conversing with guests in the adjoining family room. Entertain outdoors in the private vinyl fenced backyard with plenty of room for play. Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms including a spacious primary bathroom and hall bath for guests. This move-in ready home has all you need to make lasting memories!
